name: Interior With GAN Portrait
description:
Digital Collage by Teriell 2021

We started to search for new ideas about ourselves with the help of the machines.
Paintings and even photos of ourselves are not sufficient anymore to explain us.
We are no longer the bodies, we decided to become bigger ideas.
Reality got blurred and we continue to search for the right words to calm down our bodies.


This work is a remix of an oil painting created by Thomas Le Clear
The original file can be found at
https://www.si.edu/object/interior-portraits%3Asaam_1993.6
